---
---

<section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden bg-primary">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-25">
    <img src="/images/asparagus_cheese.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" style="object-position: center 55%;" />
  </div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15,20,25,0.9) 0%, rgba(15,20,25,0.95) 100%);"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-30" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.05) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 80px 80px;"></div>

  <div class="container-narrow relative z-10 text-center">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-6 reveal">
      <span class="block w-8 h-px bg-accent-glow"></span>
      <p class="font-outfit text-[0.6875rem] font-semibold tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-accent-glow">
        Start Cooking
      </p>
      <span class="block w-8 h-px bg-accent-glow"></span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="font-heading text-[var(--font-size-display)] text-white mb-6 reveal leading-[1.3]">
      今日の食卓を、<br />ひとつ上の体験へ。
    </h2>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-white/60 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12 reveal leading-relaxed">
      旬の食材が持つ本来の美味しさを引き出す、編集部厳選のレシピをお試しください。
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center reveal">
      <a href="/recipes/" class="btn-primary bg-white! text-primary! border-white! hover:bg-accent! hover:border-accent! hover:text-white!">
        <span>レシピを見る</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:18px">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/seasonal/" class="btn-outline border-white/30 text-white hover:border-white hover:text-white">
        四季の図鑑へ
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
